[SHORT DESC]
30% chance to poison the target.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 30% chance to poison the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Sludge is an awful competitive move, with much powerful options such as Sludge Bomb and Sludge Wave available. To make matters worse, Poison is not a very good attacking type, only hitting the Grass-type for super effective damage.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/sludge_bomb">Sludge Bomb</a> is a more powerful special Poison-type move.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/sludge_wave">Sludge Wave</a> is a more powerful special Poison-type move, with only a 10% chance of poisoning the opponent.</p>